      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) adding 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over the highest heat</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into batons</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and slice into strips</p>",
