    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped courgette</strong>, <strong>sliced pepper</strong> and<strong> diced chicken breast</strong> to the pan and cook for 10 min or until the vegetables are tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your chicken thoroughly (until there’s no pink meat and it’s piping hot!) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1674584672097-x200.jpg",
