            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the noodles are cooking, combine your<strong> peanut butter</strong>, <strong>chilli relish</strong> and 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lime[s] </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>satay sauce</strong></p><p>Cut the<strong> remaining lime</strong> into<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>1 wedge per person</p>",
