    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is cooked, add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> to the pan with the chicken and vegetables</p><p>Add the <strong>satay sauce</strong> and a splash of<strong> starchy noodle water</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Remove from the heat and stir through your<strong> toasted sesame oil </strong>– this is your <strong>nutty chicken noodle stir-fry</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
